WEBVTT

00:02:58.996 --> 00:03:01.024
And that was the aha moment.

00:03:01.524 --> 00:03:04.599
It wasn't the things I'd saved
that were important;

00:03:04.623 --> 00:03:08.173
it was the stories that went with them
that gave them meaning.

00:03:09.554 --> 00:03:12.516
Could using the objects
to tell the stories

00:03:12.540 --> 00:03:14.213
be the seed of a new ritual,

00:03:14.840 --> 00:03:18.293
a rite of passage --
not for a 13-year-old,

00:03:18.317 --> 00:03:20.656
but for someone much further
down the road?

00:03:22.468 --> 00:03:23.998
So I started experimenting.

00:03:24.683 --> 00:03:27.319
I got a few dozen things out of the boxes,

00:03:27.343 --> 00:03:28.964
I put them about in a room,

00:03:29.694 --> 00:03:31.561
and I invited people to come in